  "narrative": "<h3 class=\"story-subheading\">Short impact summary</h3>\n<p class=\"story-text\">Muddy Thinking in the Mississippi River Delta: A Call for Reclamation (2024), published by University of California Press. Sustainability & policy relevance (strength 0.6). 2035 downloads \u2014 actief gebruik.</p>\n<h3 class=\"story-subheading\">Full narrative</h3>\n<p class=\"story-text\">Muddy Thinking in the Mississippi River Delta: A Call for Reclamation was published by University of California Press in 2024. Conceptually, the work connects to Land reclamation, Mississippi delta, River delta, Delta and Hydrology (agriculture).</p>\n<p class=\"story-text\">OpenAlex records 4 citations. Citations peaked in 2024 with 2 citing works. Notable citing venues include Hydrology, Advances in global change research and Journal of Environmental Studies and Sciences. Inferred role: Sustainability & policy relevance and Scholarly uptake.</p>\n<p class=\"story-text\">2035 recorded downloads via open-access infrastructure.  SDG alignment: Climate action.</p>",
